nodes.text: MM-92-9 was a TIE pilot of the Galactic Empire.
Sometime after 0 BBY, MM-92-9 was part of a TIE pilot unit that guarded a statue of Emperor Palpatine installed in front of the Theed Royal Palace on Naboo during that year's Empire Day celebrations.
MM-92-9 was a non-player character in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. He made appearances during the Empire Day live events of 2009, 2010, and 2011.
